The paper deals with the transformation of cell complexes, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper also discusses the geometric realization of the transformed complex, which is a topic in computational geometry and topology (cs.GR). The paper presents bounds on parameters measuring geometric quality, which is a topic in computational geometry and numerical analysis (cs.DS, cs.NA). The paper also mentions an application in additive manufacturing, which falls under the category of computational manufacturing (cs.MM).
